description: This documentary depicts the days of preparation and protest at the G8 in Genoa (2001). Many directors took part in the footing, including an elderly Gillo Pontecorvo. I got the .avi from here http://www.rebeldemule.org/foro/monograf/tema972.html - unfortunately it is not easy to get Pontecorvo's films, so I am trying to help who could be interested in this great italian director.
